      "content": "You mentioned it's a \"necessary step\" for sustainable living. Some people in the city are really upset about it though, saying it's basically just a tax on people who can't afford to live in the center or those who have to drive for work. Why is the environmental benefit considered more important than the economic impact on those families?",
